'''IC 1517''' is an [[elliptical galaxy]], of apparent magnitude +13.8, in the constellation [[Pisces (constellation)|Pisces]]. The galaxy is south and west of [[Gamma Piscium]], just south of the ecliptic, and north of the constellation [[Aquarius (constellation)|Aquarius]]. It has a redshift of 0.02449.

