'''Ola David Raa Hunderi''' (born 4 February 1939) is a Norwegian physicist.

He took the [[dr.philos.]] degree in 1970, and was appointed as professor at the [[Norwegian Institute of Technology]] in 1981. From 1987 to 1993 he was the research director at [[SINTEF]].<ref name=snl>{{cite encyclopedia |year=2007 |title=Hunderi, Ola David Raa |encyclopedia=[[Store norske leksikon]] |publisher=Kunnskapsforlaget |location= |url=http://www.snl.no/article.html?id=597189 }}</ref>

